6cd761854367087cadc30df8946d208a:
mutation PhotoWithTextAndTitleEditionScreenUpdateModuleMutation(
  $webCardId: ID!
  $input: SavePhotoWithTextAndTitleModuleInput!
  $__relay_internal__pv__PixelRatiorelayprovider: Float!
  $__relay_internal__pv__ScreenWidthrelayprovider: Float!
) {
  savePhotoWithTextAndTitleModule(webCardId: $webCardId, input: $input) {
    webCard {
      id
      requiresSubscription
      cardModules {
        __typename
        kind
        visible
        ...PhotoWithTextAndTitleEditionScreen_module
        id
      }
    }
  }
}

fragment PhotoWithTextAndTitleEditionScreen_module on CardModulePhotoWithTextAndTitle {
  id
  image {
    id
    width
    height
    uri(width: $__relay_internal__pv__ScreenWidthrelayprovider, pixelRatio: $__relay_internal__pv__PixelRatiorelayprovider)
  }
  contentFontFamily
  contentFontColor
  contentTextAlign
  contentFontSize
  contentVerticalSpacing
  content
  titleFontFamily
  titleFontColor
  titleTextAlign
  titleFontSize
  titleVerticalSpacing
  title
  imageMargin
  verticalArrangement
  horizontalArrangement
  gap
  borderRadius
  marginHorizontal
  marginVertical
  aspectRatio
  background {
    id
    uri
    resizeMode
  }
  backgroundStyle {
    backgroundColor
    patternColor
  }
}
d22e0d664752b8c114d87926de1bf439:
mutation useLoadCardTemplateMutation(
  $webCardId: ID!
  $cardTemplateId: ID!
  $__relay_internal__pv__ScreenWidthrelayprovider: Float!
  $__relay_internal__pv__PixelRatiorelayprovider: Float!
) {
  loadCardTemplate(webCardId: $webCardId, cardTemplateId: $cardTemplateId) {
    webCard {
      id
      cardStyle {
        borderColor
        borderRadius
        buttonRadius
        borderWidth
        buttonColor
        fontFamily
        fontSize
        gap
        titleFontFamily
        titleFontSize
      }
      cardModules {
        __typename
        id
        visible
        ...ModuleData_cardModules
      }
    }
  }
}
